{
  "stem": "5891.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in the meantime, I found about, I was telling my dad and my sisters about what I seen in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, you know what's happening here?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a disease broke out for the children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were swelling up in the ankles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ankles were swelling up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the stomach was swelling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was some kind of disease, but they didn't know enough about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were studying that disease.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I guess the kids, they must have been dead or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took those parts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they had that all there, where they were working on that stuff.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were exposed to all those things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You sit there doing your bit, here and there, those [INAUDIBLE] looking at you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So now you just have to adapt to those things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Otherwise, you--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I thought if ever I go out again, I were not capable of loving anybody, not capable of trusting anybody.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'll tell you, I never trust anybody, really, anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Authorities, I have no trust in authorities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Never did, even the police in here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anything what has to do with authority, I am frightened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I am frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't like a policeman stopping me for anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or if he did it for any reason, there's some kind of fear comes over me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'm 70 years old, and I never left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's still there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, of course not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's not just me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everyone, my family, everyone of us who survived and are still around, we all, there's some kind of a terrible fear for the authorities situation.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because probably we felt so betrayed and never grew out of this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The four sisters, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
